file.name: chronicle.yaml
file.content:
components:
  schemas:
    tmp0:
      properties:
        asset: {type: string}
        backstoryLink: {type: string}
        name: {type: string}
        rawLog: {type: string}
        severity: {type: string}
        sourceProduct: {type: string}
        timestamp: {type: string}
        uri: {type: string}
      type: object
    tmp1:
      properties:
        asset_hostname: {type: string}
        firstSeenArtifactInfo_seenTime: {type: string}
        lastSeenArtifactInfo_artifactIndicator_domainName: {type: string}
        lastSeenArtifactInfo_seenTime: {type: string}
      type: object
    tmp2:
      properties:
        metadata_collectedTimestamp: {type: string}
        metadata_eventTimestamp: {type: string}
        metadata_eventType: {type: string}
        metadata_productName: {type: string}
        network_applicationProtocol: {type: string}
        network_dns_questions_name: {type: string}
        network_dns_questions_type: {type: string}
        principal_hostname: {type: string}
        principal_ip: {type: string}
        principal_mac: {type: string}
        target_ip: {type: string}
      type: object
    tmp3:
      properties:
        artifact_domainName: {type: string}
        firstSeenTime: {type: string}
        intRawConfidenceScore: {type: string}
        iocIngestTime: {type: string}
        lastSeenTime: {type: string}
        sources_category: {type: string}
        sources_confidenceScore_intRawConfidenceScore: {type: string}
        sources_confidenceScore_normalizedConfidenceScore: {type: string}
        sources_rawSeverity: {type: string}
        sources_source: {type: string}
      type: object
    tmp4:
      properties:
        addresses_domain: {type: string}
        addresses_port: {type: string}
        category: {type: string}
        confidenceScore_strRawConfidenceScore: {type: string}
        firstActiveTime: {type: string}
        lastActiveTime: {type: string}
        rawSeverity: {type: string}
        sourceUrl: {type: string}
      type: object
  securitySchemes: {}
info:
  contact: {email: frikky@shuffler.io, name: '@frikkylikeme', url: 'https://twitter.com/frikkylikeme'}
  description: Automated generation of Chronicle Chronicle
  title: Chronicle Chronicle
  version: 1.0.0
  x-logo: data:image/png;base64,
openapi: 3.0.2
paths:
  tmp0:
    post:
      description: Query Alerts
      parameters:
      - description: Start time for your request
        example: '2019-10-15T00:00:00Z'
        in: query
        name: start_time
        required: true
        schema: {type: string}
      - description: End time for your request
        example: '2019-10-17T00:00:00Z'
        in: query
        name: end_time
        required: true
        schema: {type: string}
      - description: Specify the maximum number of alerts to return (max. 10000)
        example: '1'
        in: query
        name: Page Size
        required: true
        schema: {type: string}
      responses:
        '200':
          content:
            application/json:
              schema: {$ref: '#/components/schemas/tmp0'}
          description: Successful request
      summary: Chronicle Query Alerts
  tmp1:
    post:
      description: Query Assets
      parameters:
      - description: Specify the artifact type ('domain_name', 'destination_ip_address',
          'hash_md5', 'hash_sha1', hash_sha256).
        example: domain_name
        in: query
        name: Artifact Type
        required: true
        schema: {type: string}
      - description: An artifact based on the Artifact Type.
        example: www.google.com
        in: query
        name: Artifact
        required: true
        schema: {type: string}
      - description: Start time for your request
        example: '2019-10-15T00:00:00Z'
        in: query
        name: Start Time
        required: true
        schema: {type: string}
      - description: End time for your request
        example: '2019-10-17T00:00:00Z'
        in: query
        name: End Time
        required: true
        schema: {type: string}
      - description: Specify the maximum number of assets to return (max. 10000)
        example: '1'
        in: query
        name: Page Size
        required: true
        schema: {type: string}
      responses:
        '200':
          content:
            application/json:
              schema: {$ref: '#/components/schemas/tmp1'}
          description: Successful request
      summary: Chronicle Query Assets
  tmp2:
    post:
      description: Query Events
      parameters:
      - description: An asset indicator can be either, 'hostname', 'asset_ip_address',
          'mac', or 'product_id'
        example: hostname
        in: query
        name: Asset Indicator
        required: true
        schema: {type: string}
      - description: An asset based on the 'Asset Indicator'
        example: bobs-pc
        in: query
        name: Asset
        required: true
        schema: {type: string}
      - description: Start time for your request
        example: '2019-11-17T20:37:00Z'
        in: query
        name: Start Time
        required: true
        schema: {type: string}
      - description: End time for your request
        example: '2019-11-18T20:37:00Z'
        in: query
        name: End Time
        required: true
        schema: {type: string}
      - description: Reference time for your request
        example: '2019-11-17T20:37:00Z'
        in: query
        name: Reference Time
        required: true
        schema: {type: string}
      - description: Specify the maximum number of Events to return (max. 10000)
        example: '1'
        in: query
        name: Page Size
        required: true
        schema: {type: string}
      responses:
        '200':
          content:
            application/json:
              schema: {$ref: '#/components/schemas/tmp2'}
          description: Successful request
      summary: Chronicle Query Events
  tmp3:
    post:
      description: List Indicators of Compromise (IOC)
      parameters:
      - description: Start time for your request
        example: '2019-10-15T20:37:00Z'
        in: query
        name: Start Time
        required: true
        schema: {type: string}
      - description: Specify the number of IoCs to return (max. 10000)
        example: '1'
        in: query
        name: Page Size
        required: true
        schema: {type: string}
      responses:
        '200':
          content:
            application/json:
              schema: {$ref: '#/components/schemas/tmp3'}
          description: Successful request
      summary: Chronicle Query IOC
  tmp4:
    post:
      description: Query Indicators of Compromise (IOC) Details
      parameters:
      - description: Specify the artifact type ('domain_name', 'destination_ip_address',
          'hash_md5', 'hash_sha1', hash_sha256).
        example: domain_name
        in: query
        name: Artifact Type
        required: true
        schema: {type: string}
      - description: ' An artifact based on the Artifact Type.'
        example: www.emjcd.com
        in: query
        name: Artifact
        required: true
        schema: {type: string}
      responses:
        '200':
          content:
            application/json:
              schema: {$ref: '#/components/schemas/tmp4'}
          description: Successful request
      summary: Chronicle Query IOC Details
tags:
- {name: SIEM & Log Management}
